README File

The Movie Trailer Website project consists of 3 files

Media.py - This file contains the movie class that outlines the characteristics of a movie.
Entertainment_center.py - This file creates the movie elements for movies that will be on the website. It then calls a function to create the website with the movie trailers and information displayed
fresh_tomatoes.py - This file defines the layout and the style of the trailers website. It also creates the html file for the website and places the Movie elements on the page.

To generate the movie trailer website, run the following command after python is in the classpath

python entertainment_center.py


NOTE - Additional features beyond basic project requirements
- Added rating and year of release
- Added error checks for rating and year of release
- Sorted movies in order of release date
- Added movie storyline in mouseover and error image if the image does not load

